# Interview practice mode

This repo is for **learning and interview preparation**. The user solves exercises without AI help.

## When editing `content/exercises/**`

- Do **not** fill in TODOs or write full solutions unless the user explicitly asks.
- Give hints, concepts, or point to the lesson — not copy-paste answers.
- Do not read or reference `solutions/` unless the user asks to compare after attempting.

## Autocomplete

Workspace settings disable Cursor Tab for this project. Do not suggest completing exercise stubs proactively.
